  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "植物や動物の時代の前、地球は完全に暗闇に包まれ、今私たちが「モンスター」と呼ぶ存在が住んでいました。「光あれ」という声が響いたとき、多くのモンスターはこの新しい光の世界では生きられず、命を落としました。しかし、全てが死んだわけではありません。中には洞窟に隠れ、力を蓄えた者たちもいました。今、彼らは再びこの世界に戻りたいと願っており、あなたはその時代の中で生きています。\n\n14歳の誕生日に、亡き父の剣と盾を授かります。これであなたは試練に挑む準備が整い、もしかしたら、あなた自身が英雄になることができるかもしれません。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Millions of years ago, heinous creatures that lurked in the shadows and darkness that blanketed the planet inhabited the Earth. When light finally broke through, only a few beasts were able to survive by burrowing into deep caverns. Over time, they multiplied, evolved, and patiently waited for the right time to emerge and rule the Earth once again. You are Corona, and you've just celebrated your 14th birthday. By law of the king, you must now go seek out these creatures of the dark and destroy them. As you travel in search of your destiny, you'll make animal allies that will prove invaluable on your quest. Each level will offer mind-bending puzzles and challenges that will help you get one step closer to completing your mission.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
